sg":"立法會主席？"},{"pid":"fe7d7e584a23e7d3a26abe35f7a237a088c8a3d0","tid":1242411,"uid":27605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:34:18.000Z","msg":"政制及內地事務局局長 我估"},{"pid":"21fdbf140a86b0817c1c0299c79390538ac9090d","tid":1242411,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:34:54.000Z","msg":"追究 警察濫權濫用武力 先係我地依家既王牌！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242366\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242366</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f00d021575bce33bc516eec5c550c3ef57564a","tid":1242411,"uid":45082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9e6cacd2e4a45c74df2c29973997ecdb454cb3b","tid":1242411,"uid":57787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:29:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政務司<span style=\"color: red;\">司長</span>]休假嘅話，會喺under政務司資歷最耐嘅局長署任。<br />\n<br />\n我估照跟</blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:36:07.000Z","msg":"我一直都以為係財政司署任"},{"pid":"e82e9d3160d9d9ddaa0589ea2ef6132a5eb31646","tid":1242411,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e03d4e46ef4591e112f2324c5c787dc5b269c5f4","tid":1242411,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29b6be7e88b58176dfbb208a004fb154e42cec3f","tid":1242411,"uid":14103,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:09:56.000Z","msg":"可能葉劉會借d耳行埋個度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:31:02.000Z","msg":"借完點還"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:37:20.000Z","msg":"破產"},{"pid":"59557ff677ebcd752b1d1c3ab35a4507483b6e69","tid":1242411,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:38:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.protocol.gov.hk/images/chi/precedence/Precedence_List_20190601.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.protocol.gov.hk%2Fimages%2Fchi%2Fprecedence%2FPrecedence_List_20190601.pdf&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=271650ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.protocol.gov.hk/images/chi/precedence/Precedence_List_20190601.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"302dafb89f0c1b0907226ce73332dce267f1026c","tid":1242411,"uid":28792,"like":